====FREE-HEAT
Mirrors direct solar to heat forge/furnace/oven areas and for hot water.
Wood-chip stove provides continuous heat from shredded tree trimmings.
Massive hopper holds enough for 3 months of hands-free operation.
If we have all the fruit and nut trees we need, the fuel is free.
